#ROOM
Vnum     18040
Name     &YThe Gates of Zul'Farrak&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The blinding glare of the Tanaris sun is partially blocked by 
massive sandstone pillars. A shimmering, heat-distorted portal 
stands between the jagged desert rocks and the ancient city of 
the Sandfury trolls. The air is dry and smells of old incense 
and scorched earth.
~
Exit
Direction out~
ToRoom    33001
Desc      Return to the Tanaris desert.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    18041
Desc      The path leads into the city streets.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     18041
Name     &YThe Sand-Swept Thoroughfare&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Ancient stone pavers are nearly buried under drifting dunes. To 
the north, the city opens up into a wide plaza. High stone walls 
on either side are carved with the fierce visages of troll gods.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    18040
Desc      The entrance gates.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    18042
Desc      The thoroughfare continues.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 18001 10 18041
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     18042
Name     &YThe Great Plaza of the Sun&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This massive open-air square is the heart of the lower city. 
Tunnels branch off in several directions. To the west, the 
sound of hissing suggests a beast's lair, while the north 
leads toward the sacred temples.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    18041
Desc      The thoroughfare.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    18043
Desc      The path to Antu'sul.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    18047
Desc      The path to the temple district.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 18000 10 18042
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     18043
Name     &yThe Basilisk Trails - Entry&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The well-maintained stone of the plaza gives way to jagged 
rock and loose sand. Large, multi-legged tracks are visible 
in the dust, leading deeper into the western canyons.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    18042
Desc      Return to the plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    18044
Desc      The trail continues.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 18003 10 18043
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
