#ROOM
Vnum     18047
Name     &YThe Temple District - Main Way&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here is more grand. Gold leaf accents the 
sandstone walls, and braziers of blue fire burn eternally at 
the intersections. To the east, a gloomy path leads toward 
the city's necropolis.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    18042
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
