Vnum     18048
Name     &wThe Path of Ancestors - East&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The transition to the graveyard is marked by a sudden drop in 
temperature. The air is still, and the only sound is the 
faint rattle of bone charms hanging from the walls.
~
Exit
Direction west~
