Sector   field~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This wide, sandy basin is filled with hundreds of shallow 
graves. The ground is soft and seems to churn with a life 
of its own. Witch Doctor Zum'rah stands at the far end, 
conducting a dark ritual.
~
Exit
Direction west~
